{"tid":1668248,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（清算師召喚）舉報鐘雅倫，隨時有橫財","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T02:19:00.000Z","uid":47202,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1063cd4316502509762d5edca4be45332a0fb0e0","tid":1668248,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"隱藏海外收入的後果 (Consequences for Evading Taxes on Foreign Source Income)<br />\n如果國稅局發現您有未申報的收入或未申報的國外金融帳戶，您將面臨嚴重後果。這些後果可能不只須補繳額外的稅金，還可能包括高額罰金，利息，罰款甚至坐牢。<br />\n<br />\n舉報推銷海外逃漏稅辦法的促銷員 (Reporting Promoters of Off-Shore Tax Avoidance Schemes)<br />\n國稅局鼓勵您舉報推銷海外逃漏稅辦法的促銷員。向國稅局舉報並提供稅務欺詐罪行情資的告密者應填寫211表 &rdquo;舉報稅務詐欺情資獎金申請書&rdquo;(Application for Award for Original Information)，並按照2008-4號通知【依7623法規向國稅局密告辦公室提出獎賞要求】(Claims Submitted to the IRS Whistleblower Office under Section 7623)列出的步驟進行就有資格獲得獎金。"},{"pid":"76f06b4836e35da820f9c40354f3d4cdffee4b55","tid":1668248,"uid":47202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"快啲清算，隨時有搵番筆。"},{"pid":"6acc788c24ab95e141adfa19883d9c5f8ccb4345","tid":1668248,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f473199b3adfa900781ea88cd87704ee70d1a6","tid":1668248,"uid":21095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2037d861bcfb312d8126e50653fda951b5c11c8","tid":1668248,"uid":21095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f2f189991d4c4ff7f49e59b255d6ccc4